SQL_STMT_U.val: select DocEntry, ObjType,docStatus,canceled,FinncPriod from ordr where (CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and datasource = 'S' and DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and (canceled = ':6' or ':6' is null or ':6' = '') and (U_IDU_Kode_PT = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') order by DocEntry Desc

select b.DocDate as 'Doc Date', DocNum as 'Doc Num', CardName as 'Customer', U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee', trim(REPLACE(Comments,char(13),' ')) as 'Comments', case when DocStatus = 'O' then 'Open' else 'Close' end as 'Status', ItemCode as 'Item Code', Dscription as 'Item Name', Quantity, UomCode as 'Uom' , U_IDU_QtyPack as 'Qty Pack', U_IDU_UOMPack as 'Uom Pack', WhsCode as 'Warehouse' from DLN1 as A join ODLN as B on a.DocEntry = b.DocEntry Where (CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (B.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and datasource = 'S' and DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and U_IDU_Kode_PT like ':6' and canceled <> 'C' and (Canceled = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '')

SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.DocDate as 'Posting Date' ,T0.DocNum as 'Document Number' ,T0.CardName as 'Customer Name' ,TRIM(REPLACE(T0.numatcard,char(59),'')) as 'Customer Reference' ,T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee' ,T1.Dscription as 'Item Name' ,T1.U_IDU_QtyPack as 'Qty Pack' ,T1.U_IDU_UOMPack as 'UOM Pack' ,T1.Quantity as 'Qty' ,T1.unitMsr as 'UOM Qty' ,T1.WhsCode as 'Warehouse' ,Trim(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(T0.comments,char(13),''),char(10),''),Char(59),'')) as 'Remarks' ,T0.DocStatus as 'Status' ,T1.basetype as 'Base Document' ,T1.baseref as 'Base Number' from ODLN T0 join DLN1 T1 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry where (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and T0.canceled <> 'C' :8 :2 :3 :1 :6 :7 :9 :10 :11 order by T0.docentry desc
